description: Try your hand at this Chinese hoisin stir-fry with beef and garlic. No surprises here, this easy 20-minute recipe is a winner when it comes to mid-week meals.
keywords: Stir-fry,Broccolini,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Low salt,Low sugar,Beef
name: Chinese Hoisin & Garlic Stir Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 45g Five Tastes Stir Fry Shot - Chinese Hoisin & Garlic

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a non-stick wok or frypan over medium-high heat. Add Stir fry Beef and stir-fry for 1 minute.
Add vegetables to wok and continue to stir fry for 2-3 minutes
Stir in contents of Five Tastes Stir Fry Shot and cook for 1 minute. Serve immediately garnished with spring onion slices.
Serve with 440g of noodles (cooked as per the instruction on pack).
